   <title>NCEP CPC Upper Stratospheric and Lower Mesospheric Analyses</title>
   <summary>
      <p>The Global Upper Stratospheric and Lower Mesospheric Analyses are provided on a pair of 65 by 65 polar grids, daily at 12Z. These were operationally prepared by NCEP/CPC, using Advanced Microwave Sounding Unit (AMSU) satellite data.</p>
      <p>The analyses are available on four levels: 5, 2, 1 and 0.4 millibars. Parameters include pressure, geopotential height, and temperature.</p>
   </summary>
